HEADWORD: ceibo
<hw>ceibo</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a small South American spiny tree
(<spn>Erythrina crista-galli</spn>) with dark crimson and scarlet
flowers solitary or clustered.</def>⟦br⟧
